<s> Hughes Aircraft Co. , a unit of General Motors Corp. , said it agreed to purchase the Electro-Optics Technology division of Perkin-Elmer Corp . </s>
<s> Terms of the agreement were n't disclosed . </s>
<s> But for the fiscal year ended July 31 , 1988 , the most recent period for which results were broken out , the Perkin-Elmer unit accounted for more than half the $ 145 million in sales recorded by the company 's government systems sector . </s>
<s> Perkin-Elmer , which is based in Norwalk , Conn. , said the sale of the Danbury , Conn. , unit is consistent with its restructuring strategy announced in April . </s>
<s> In addition to making electro-optical systems , the unit also makes laser warning receivers . </s>
<s> These are used aboard military helicopters to warn pilots that a laser weapon has been focused on them . </s>
<s> Hughes of Los Angeles said the PerkinElmer unit 's work complements efforts by its Electro-Optical and Data Systems group , which makes infrared sensors , military lasers and night vision equipment . </s>
<s> Hughes said it expects the sale to close by year end . </s>
